y: \'Times New Roman\';\">They provide <strong>website design and development</strong>. Their websites are <strong>attractive, fast, and simple</strong> for users. They also work on <strong>Shopify development</strong>, including <strong>setting up stores and creating custom themes</strong> for online shops.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Qonkar helps businesses grow online with <a href=\"https://qonkar.com/services/branding-and-performance-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>digital marketing</strong></a>. This includes <a href=\"https://qonkar.com/services/branding-and-performance-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>SEO</strong></a>, <a href=\"https://qonkar.com/services/branding-and-performance-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>paid advertising</strong></a>, and <a href=\"https://qonkar.com/services/branding-and-performance-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>content marketing</strong></a> to reach more customers.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">They also make <a href=\"https://qonkar.com/services/software-development\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>mobile apps</strong></a> for iOS and Android. These include <strong>automotive apps</strong> (for cars), <strong>on-demand apps</strong> (for services like delivery), <strong>real estate apps</strong> (for property), <strong>healthcare apps</strong>, <strong>e-commerce apps</strong>, and <strong>music apps</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: au